
'square [ dup * ] def
5 square 25 == check
'square word? true == check
'square body [ dup * ] == check
'square see "'square [ dup * ] def" == check
'square doc "'square [ dup * ] def" == check

\ Repeated execution resolves the same parsed call object.
'cache-target [ 1 ] def
'cache-run [ cache-target ] def
10 [ cache-run 1 == check ] times

\ Redefinition replaces a word's implementation.
'cache-target [ 2 ] def
10 [ cache-run 2 == check ] times

\ More than one cache's worth of dynamic call objects exercise eviction while
\ each retained cache key continues to resolve by its own name.
'cache-one [ 1 ] def
'cache-two [ 2 ] def
100 [
    'cache-one >call exec 1 == check
    'cache-two >call exec 2 == check
] times
